the lush bowl of couscous. Sitting on top are the tender beef strips. A chilled yoghurt dolloped on top will have you
feeling refreshed in no time.

*Unfortunately, this
week's silverbeet was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with baby
spinach. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
